headline: HEICO's Q1 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Sales Increase Y/Y
summary: HEI's total revenues in the fourth quarter of 2024 beat the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 6.1%. The top line also increases 14.9% from the year-ago level.
